title: Ultimate Chicken Wing Combo Garlic Parm, Buffalo & Cajun | 6 Servings
description: The best way to celebrate Father’s Day is with a cookout. Is there anything more cookout-worthy than chicken wings? The answer is no! This combo comes with three finger-licking flavors: The first 18 ounces of wings are coated in garlic, herbs, and Parmesan, the second in a spicy buffalo spice and brown sugar rub, and the third in savory, kickin’ Cajun-style spices. Once baked, these wings are perfectly crispy on the outside and super juicy on the inside. The only question is whether to dip them in blue cheese or ranch! (Additional ingredients not included.)

